        Vars.obsvp = macros1.either(4, 5, 6);
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"I have peered into the darkness and seen the blackness of men's souls. They shamble forward in my dreams, like fresh corpses wreathed in a haze of putrefaction. Their cold hands clutch at my nightgown. When they have surrounded me fully with their numbers, filling my vision with a wall of decaying flesh - that is when I awake again, screaming.");
