            "s and he would be called a kind-hearted soul. Now there are far too many papers " +
            "to sign.\"");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("\"The Asylum is in a financially precarious position. If they offer you an opportu" +
            "nity to invest, simply refuse and I will provide free labor for your troubles.\"");
