            yield return text(@"While seemingly innocuous, our amazingly versatile fabric that could not be stained also appeared to have the more important side effect of repelling all possible stain sources with vicious force. Upon offering our fabric as a possible alternative for the town's flag, the light cloth explosively began to ascend and descend in mid-air, flapping wildly about the room. We fled City Hall and watched in mild amusement and terror as the experiment destroyed the building entirely within seconds.");
        }
        if (Vars.ex == "eng")
        {
            yield return text("Experiment Notes - A Robot Servant That Prepares Meals with Lasers: ");
            yield return lineBreak(); //br tag
            yield return text(@"Possibly a flawed idea from the beginning and admittedly not our best overall craftsmanship, the robot butler almost immediately began to indscriminantly fire lasers literally everywhere. Our demonstration was very brief in City Hall, before we all retreated to a safer distance and observed the easily avoidable chaos that we had caused. The City Hall was engulfed in flames in minutes. Dreadful, really.");
        }
        if (Vars.ex == "bio")
        {
            yield return text("Experiment Notes - Injecting an Agitated Gorilla with Hormones and Radium: ");
            yield return lineBreak(); //br tag
            yield return text(@"The cage in which our great primate was displayed was woefully inadequate, and upon the slightest provocation it emerged violently from its enclosure at the very beginning of our exhibition at City Hall. Covered in a disturbing amount of blood and viscera within seconds, the inevitable mistake rampaged through the room in a whirlwind of coffee and silver fur. We exited hastily to observe from a more appropriate distance as a hailstorm of shattered bones showered the nearby streets.");
        }
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("However, undaunted, the Experiment continued its path of destruction until we wer" +
            "e able to subdue it with our hastily prepared antidotal serum.");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        using (styleScope("hook", "h00254"))
            yield return link("Click to see if the Experiment\'s rampage continues...", null, () => enchantHook("h00254", HarloweEnchantCommand.Replace, passage213_Fragment_0));
        Vars.dev = 16;
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield break;
    }

