            " if it were the last I will ever read.");
            yield return lineBreak();
            yield return lineBreak();

        }
        else if (Vars.nameA == Vars.fate3)
        {
            yield return text(@"I have spent days upon days locked away within my secret laboratory. It is as though my entire existence is singularly focused on the pursuit of scientific excellence. I do not care if it drives me mad! If my contributions can advance Science even by a minute amount it will all be worth it!");
            yield return lineBreak();
            yield return lineBreak();

        }
        else if (Vars.nameA == Vars.fate4)
        {
            yield return text("I am surrounded by simple-minded human filth. How dare they look at such an afflu" +
