            "stocrat\'s greatest, most valuable work? Oh, they will PAY for their insolence!");
            yield return lineBreak();
            yield return lineBreak();

        }
        else if (Vars.nameA == Vars.fate5)
        {
            yield return text("I will not suffer fools. It is just as important for a peasant or a king to know " +
            "their place in the presence of my genius. I will show them ");
            using (styleScope("bold", true))
            {
                yield return text("all");
            }
            yield return text(" how to pay homage to their betters. Soon there will be no way to ignore my inspir" +
            "ational presence and I will command respect!");
            yield return lineBreak();
            yield return lineBreak();

        }
        else //if (Vars.nameA == Vars.fate6)
        {
            yield return text(@"I find pleasure in the simple act of experimentation. Every tested hypothesis is a delectable morsel to be savored. And is it not my obligation - my right - to share this sense of wonder with the world? The wretches deserve to be entertained - for what is life without spectacle and indulgence?");
            yield return lineBreak();
            yield return lineBreak();

        }
