        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("I think it is high time for an innovative, aggressive new program to be introduce" +
            "d. I have scheduled a meeting with the Asylum\'s director. You do not need to wis" +
            "h me luck. I will be persuasive. A change is on the horizon.");
